name: Stanton House El Paso
description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at Stanton House El Paso! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.
Located in El Paso, a 6-minute walk from El Paso Museum of Art, Stanton House El Paso provides accommodations with a shared lounge, private parking, a terrace and a bar. With a fitness center, the 4-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The property has room service, an ATM and luggage storage for guests.
Guest rooms at the hotel are equipped with a flat-screen TV with cable channels and a safety deposit box. At Stanton House El Paso each room comes with bed linen and towels.
The daily breakfast offers à la carte, continental or American options. At the accommodation you'll find a restaurant serving French and Mexican cuisine. Vegetarian, vegan and dairy-free options can also be requested.
Ironing facilities, and a business center are available, as well as a 24-hour front desk.
Ciudad Juarez Cathedral is 2.1 miles from Stanton House El Paso, while Benito Juarez Olympic Stadium is 2.3 miles away. The nearest airport is El Paso International Airport, 6.2 miles from the hotel.

userReviews.title: The hotel is located in a great location w/ many restaurants, bars, and attractions around the area.
userReviews.positive:
My family (a group of 6) had brunch on Sunday afternoon at the hotel. It was pricey, but delicious. The orange juice was freshly squeezed and all plates were served fresh off the stove. 
As for our room - all in all it was very comfortable and quiet. The mini bar was stocked with soft drinks, beer, water, and even multiple full size liquor bottles - which all came at the typical higher price you usually encounter at hotels. 
Lastly, I appreciated the extra security my room key offered as every night the front doors of the hotel would lock at around 10pm and ultimately the only access to the hotel was offered by your own key card. In other words, you couldn't enter the hotel past 10pm without a key.
userReviews.negative:
During checkout, I found the lady at the front desk to be quite rude to me. As I approached the desk that morning she looked me straight in the eyes, rolled her own eyes, and then proceeded to ask me in a mildly annoyed way what room I had been staying in. I found her to be unnecessarily cold and ill-mannered - something that I do not usually encounter when I stay at high quality hotels. This is completely unacceptable to me and I hope that in the future hotel management can provide better training to these individuals who deal with customers on a daily basis. 
Another drawback was the fact that the hotel does not provide a clothing iron or ironing board. The hotel only provides a steamer. Luckily, the staff was able to locate an iron for me, however no ironing board was included. My husband had to iron his clothes on the floor. 
Also, the shower floor is extremely slippery. I would not feel comfortable allowing anyone who is older to shower alone.

userReviews.title: Disappointing - no advantage over an airbnb rental
userReviews.positive: The executive suite was very large with a good table, couch, chairs, and desk. We could have had seats for 10 people in there and plenty of room for more. I liked the big bottles of shampoo, conditioner and bath gel in the shower (instead of little bottles that run out quickly and fall off the soap shelf).  The bed was comfortable. The Breakfast was adequate with both hot and cold foods, about the middle range compared to other places we have stayed.
userReviews.negative:
They had staffing problems. One night we ran out of toilet paper, we called down to the desk and no one answered. We went down, and no one was there. Finally we took some toilet paper from the public bathroom. They say you can call for anything you need, but based on our experience that means only during the day. What if it had been something worse? I can understand if they can't find employees, but shouldn't the manager or the owner fill in the gaps?
They also only clean each floor once a week which is probably due to staffing problems. I was OK with that, but they expect you to bag up your trash and take it down the hall each day. There was even a sign telling us not to put loose trash in the can, but instead to break down boxes and bag it all up. So no cleaning, bag up and haul your own trash according to their rules, and no supplies unless you are there while staff are on duty. My issue is that it felt like I was paying full price while missing services. We stayed at other suite hotels this vacation, also with staffing issues, who handled it much better.
There were several little things that lowered my rating as well. The power plugs at the desk were loose so that my plugs didn't always make a connection. I had to charge stuff at the kitchen counter. The couch needed some pillows to make it more comfortable to sit on. The chair in the bedroom had its seat cushion cover coming off due to a ripped seam. The bedroom had no light tied to its switch by the door. You should have at least one light tied to that switch so people don't have to fumble in the dark looking for a lamp or light switch that works. The same was true in the living room (a switch by the door that did nothing). There were no pots and pans for cooking (So, how useful is a full kitchen if you don't have anything to cook with?) I thought a hotel would have a more reliably functional space, and more in person help and services than an airbnb of a similar price.

name: Homewood Suites by Hilton El Paso Airport
description:
This all-suite El Paso hotel is located minutes from El Paso International Airport and Fort Bliss. The hotel has a putting green and guest suites with full kitchens.
El Paso Homewood Suites provides a hot breakfast every morning. Guests can use the gym, racquetball court, or outdoor pool.  Other available services include a 24-hour market, business center, and laundry facilities.
Guest suites at Homewood Suites El Paso have free Wi-Fi and cable TV. The spacious suites feature a living area and the kitchens include a stove, full refrigerator, and dishwasher.
Major corporations, including Boeing and Delphi, are a 15-minute drive from Homewood Suites El Paso Airport. Also within a 10-minute drive of the hotel are the El Paso Zoo and the El Paso Museum of History.

name: The Hotel at Sunland Park Casino El Paso, Ascend Hotel Collection
description:
Located 6.6 miles from El Paso Museum of Art, The Hotel at Sunland Park Casino El Paso, Ascend Hotel Collection offers 2-star accommodations in El Paso and has a casino. Featuring a fitness center, the 2-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The hotel has an ATM machine and a fax machine and photocopier that guests can use.
The rooms at the hotel come with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels and a safety deposit box. At The Hotel at Sunland Park Casino El Paso, Ascend Hotel Collection rooms have bed linen and towels.

Ciudad Juarez Cathedral is 8.5 miles from the accommodation, while Benito Juarez Olympic Stadium is 8.7 miles from the property. The nearest airport is El Paso International Airport, 14 miles from The Hotel at Sunland Park Casino El Paso, Ascend Hotel Collection.

name: Hilton Garden Inn El Paso Airport
description:
Located along Interstate 10, this hotel offers free transfers to El Paso International Airport, just 2 miles away.  It features an on-site restaurant, a 24-hour convenience store and an outdoor pool.
A flat-screen TV and free Wi-Fi are provided in each room at Hilton Garden Inn Airport El Paso.  The traditionally styled rooms feature warm colors and offer a microwave, fridge and coffee-making facilities.
El Paso Hilton Garden Inn offers casual American cuisine at Great American Grill & Pavilion Lounge.  A full bar and room service are also offered.
Guests can work out in the on-site fitness room or work in the business center.  Guest laundry facilities are also available.
The hotel is less than 10 minutes’ drive from Chamizal National Memorial and El Paso city center.  El Paso Zoo is 4 miles away.

name: Residence Inn El Paso
description:
Residence Inn El Paso is located 2 miles from El Paso Airport. It offers an indoor pool and air-conditioned guestrooms with a 32-inch flat-screen cable TV.
Fully-equipped kitchens provide a stovetop, refrigerator, and a dishwasher. A seating area is included with all rooms. Room service is also available.
A well-equipped gym, with free weights and cardiovascular equipment, is provided by Residence Inn El Paso for guests that like to keep fit. Free Wi-Fi is offered throughout the hotel.
Free public parking is available. The hotel is a 10-minute drive from Fort Bliss, the El Paso Zoo is just 4 miles from this hotel and Old Mission Trail is 10.4 miles away. Sun Bowl Stadium is 10 minutes away by car.

userReviews.positive: we love the food here. the staff, for the most part, is very attentive and they go out of their way to make sure our stay is nothing but perfect.
userReviews.negative:
the first day, the lady at the counter asked if I wanted to switch to a different room. I asked if the room was the same size, to what she replied “no” and added that it was in fact smaller.
why would I want to switch to a smaller room, which is cheaper, after I paid for the bigger one.
then she refused to give me breakfast vouchers for the kids, even though I got the breakfast included, because “kids eat free”.. sadly, my kids don’t eat from the kids menu anymore.
the last day I ordered a skillet which was supposed to come with peppers, mushrooms, and eggs, and it didn’t have any of these! it only had bacon, ham and potatoes. luckily, they didn’t have an issue remaking my order.
also, the young girl Saturday morning made it right and gave me the vouchers for my kiddos for breakfast.
It’s upsetting coming in and for someone to be rude or to give you an attitude when you’re simply asking a question.. I’ve always said, if you don’t like your job, Quit!
I’m glad the employees that were there from Saturday morning till Sunday afternoon at checkout made it better. Both the staff at the front desk and the girls at the restaurant & bar were great!
thanks for picking up the slack! Love this location.

name: Hyatt Place El Paso Airport
description:
Free WiFi is among one of the many the convenient amenities offered at Hyatt Place El Paso Airport. The shops at Bassett Place Mall are 10 minutes' walk away.
A seating area and a satellite TV with access to pay-per-view channels are provided in each room at El Paso Airport Hyatt Place. The rooms also come with a refrigerator. Free toiletries and a hairdryer are included in the private bathroom.
You can dine at the Hyatt Place El Paso Airport's on-site restaurant. A free airport shuttle and a free shuttle service to the surrounding area are offered for your convenience. Free parking and a 24-hour front desk are available.
The International Bridge of the Americas is 3.5 miles from the hotel. El Paso International Airport is 6 minutes' drive away.

name: Embassy Suites by Hilton El Paso
description:
Located in El Paso's business district, only moments from major corporations and El Paso International Airport, this all-suite hotel features free Wi-Fi.
The spacious accommodations at the Embassy Suites by Hilton El Paso provides guests with comfortable 2-room suites furnished with a cable TV and in-room safe. A microwave, refrigerator and coffee machine are also included. Private bathrooms include a hairdryer and ironing facilities.
The hotel offers a complimentary, buffet breakfast and an evening reception featuring beer, wine, premium spirits and light snacks.
Within 10 miles from El Paso Suites Hotel, guests can find the corporate offices of Boeing, Delphi and Siemens. Sunland Park Racetrack and Casino is 15 minutes' drive away.

name: The Soluna Hotel
description:
Offering an outdoor pool and a fitness center, this El Paso hotel is 2 miles from El Paso Zoo.
Each air-conditioned guest room at The Soluna Hotel is furnished with a cable TV, a microwave, and a work desk.  A hairdryer and free toiletries are provided in the private bathroom.
The Soluna Hotel has a 24-hour front desk to serve guests at all times.  A vending machine and luggage storage are also available.
Guests can enjoy sweeping mountain views at Wyler Aerial Tramway, 6 miles from the hotel.  Soluna is 5 minutes' drive from El Paso International Airport.

name: Courtyard By Marriott El Paso Downtown/Convention Center
description:
Located in El Paso, a 4-minute walk from El Paso Museum of Art, Courtyard By Marriott El Paso Downtown/Convention Center has accommodations with free bikes, private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness center. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a shared lounge and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Chamizal Park is 3.6 miles away and Monumento a la Mexicanidad is 6.6 miles from the hotel.
At the hotel rooms contain air conditioning and a flat-screen TV.
Courtyard By Marriott El Paso Downtown/Convention Center offers an à la carte or American breakfast.
The accommodation has a sun terrace.
Guests can use the business center or relax in the bar.
Ciudad Juarez Cathedral is 2.3 miles from Courtyard By Marriott El Paso Downtown/Convention Center, while Benito Juarez Olympic Stadium is 2.5 miles from the property. The nearest airport is El Paso International Airport, 6.2 miles from the hotel.

userReviews.title: Comfortable Hostel at an Amazing Price
userReviews.positive: The price is amazing, especially since there wasn't anyone else in the room with me (I booked the hostel dorm room) and I got it all to myself. :) I liked the downtown location, making the area very walkable. And you get discounts at the near bars / restaurants by showing your room key.
userReviews.negative:
First off, the parking situation is very, very misleading on the posting. This is a downtown hotel / hostel, which means street parking or lots. The "free parking" offered onsite, is two, yes TWO, free spaces in front of the hotel. And usually when someone parks there, they don't move for a couple of days. So plan to pay for metered street parking or close lots / garages if you have a car. 
Only other things I would mention as FYI: older hotel that uses evaporative cooling, meaning there's no AC unit in the room. Instead there's a transom over the doors and you open your window to create air flow. I was comfortable, but others may not be. The hostel rooms back into the bars / restaurants and you can hear the music until bars close at 2 AM (almost like being there, it's that loud) - just be aware if this isn't your thing. And finally, there are no elevators, two flights of stairs up to the female dorms (like 50 steps LOL) so pack light.

userReviews.title: Good stay overall
userReviews.positive: The property is very charming with a vintage feel. It is extremely clean! The shared facilities are nice. The front desk agent was super friendly and helpful, I wish I got his name. They offer great deals at nearby bars and restaurants.
userReviews.negative: I didn’t realize we wouldn’t have AC (the main description on booking says cooling and TVs are in each room), the fan was okay but it still felt quite hot at night.
userReviews.room: Room with One Double Bed with Shared Bathroom

name: Quality Inn Airport East
description:
The Quality Inn Airport East hotel is located just minutes from the El Paso International Airport, Juarez, Mexico and Fort Bliss. Additional area attractions include the El Paso Zoo and Insights El Paso Science Museum. Several restaurants and shopping centers are within walking distance of this hotel. The Cielo Vista Mall is only two miles away.
Guests will enjoy the following amenities: free airport transportation from 7 am to 11 pm, free wireless high-speed Internet access, free 24-hour coffee and free to go breakfast. Be sure to enjoy our large outdoor pool and hot tub surrounded by beautiful landscaping. This hotel also offers free local calls.
Business travelers to this Texas hotel will appreciate access to copy and fax services. The on-site meeting room accommodates most events and business functions. All guest rooms have microwaves, refrigerators, coffee makers, cable television with free HBO, hair dryers, irons and ironing boards. Nonsmoking rooms can be requested. A laundry facility is located on the premises for guest use.

name: Comfort Suites El Paso West
description:
Located just off the intersection of I-10 and Highway 20, this El Paso hotel features a heated indoor pool and a whirlpool. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the hotel.
All guest suites have microwaves, refrigerators, flat-screen televisions, coffee makers, curved shower rods, hair dryers, irons, ironing boards, voice mail, sofa sleepers and cable television.
Guests have free access to a fitness room overlooking the pool. Last-minute work can be completed in the business center, featuring public use computers and copy/fax services.  The on-site banquet and meeting room can accommodate up to 50 people for most business or social functions.
A continental breakfast, including cereals, baked goods and fresh fruit, is served at the West El Paso Comfort Suites each morning.
Coin-operated laundry facilities are located on the premises and valet cleaning service is offered. On-site parking is available and can accommodate most cars, trucks and buses.
The Comfort West El Paso is less than 10 miles from the University of Texas El Paso and less than 30 minutes from the El Paso International Airport.

We arrived/paid, but when we got to the room it was not ready. The door was open and there where no beds in there at all. Next the TV wasn’t working(turned out to have been disconnected from the back) which I fixed and turned on myself. My point was when I asked 3 of the staff members this was there reply, 
Housekeeping said, “go get it, that is not my job”. 
Other housekeeping said, “well idk go to the front, that’s not part of my job”. 
Went to the room and called and the reply was the same “I can’t leave front desk, you can come for it”. 
Then, we where told to get out the pool at 10pm(which we did about 5mins before). At 11:15 me and my kids go to get some drinks and the pool was full. When I asked the front desk he said “no I told you 11”. 
Then walked off and went to tell them to get out. 
When it clearly said 10pm on the door and they had already told us about the time! 🤔 
I loved the place and would have loved for our experience to have been different. It was supposed to have been our family little get a way 😔 
I did tell the person at the front desk and he said “you can talk to someone tomorrow”. 
I was born and raised in El Paso, I expected a little better 😔 my kids where devastated .

name: Fairfield Inn and Suites by Marriott El Paso
description:
This El Paso, Texas hotel is an 8-minute drive from the Western Playland Amusement Park. The hotel offers a continental breakfast and guest accommodations include a 32-inch flat-screen TV.
Every room at the Fairfield Inn and Suites by Marriott El Paso provides free Wi-Fi. The rooms offer a microwave and a mini-refrigerator. A separate living area with a sofa bed is available in select suites.
The Fairfield Inn and Suites El Paso features an indoor pool and a fitness room. Free coffee is available in the lobby and the hotel includes laundry facilities.
The Franklin Mountains State Park and the El Paso International Airport are a 20-minute drive from the Fairfield Inn El Paso. Guided tours are available to nearby Juarez, Mexico.

description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at Chase Suite El Paso! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.
Set in El Paso, Chase Suite El Paso provides a fitness center. Featuring barbecue facilities, this 3-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with a private bathroom. The hotel also offers free WiFi as well as a free airport shuttle service.
The units in the hotel are equipped with a flat-screen TV with cable channels. Selected rooms are equipped with a kitchen with a dishwasher. All units at Chase Suite El Paso are fitted with a seating area.

userReviews.title: Best hotel that meets all my requirements, especially when traveling with my rabbit.
userReviews.positive:
- Pet friendly.
- Apartment style living.
- Car can be parked close to your 'house' which makes unloading easier.
- Lots of privacy.
- Rooms are big! Has a kitchen with plates/utensils/pan/microwave/oven etc. Fyi, no condiments. Tv area with sofa and low table. Dining table with high chairs and a work table with a work chair too. 
- Toilets are well separated. Vanity outside and bathing/toilet bowl inside separated by a door. 
- Breakfast is simple but very sufficient for a full meal. Skillet eggs/bacon taste nice too. 
- As we were travelling with my rabbit, carpet cleanliness was of utmost importance as she's closest to the ground. I was very relieved upon entering the room. 
- I'll choose chase over any higher star hotel. 
- Usual staffs were friendly. We checked in after midnight, and the counter lady was still smiley even at that hour.
userReviews.negative: Staffs deployed on 4 July (holiday) wasn't friendly in comparison to the usual staffs. Guy that was managing the breakfast was just drawing on his piece of paper just behind the food counter even when people started coming in. No smiles, no greetings and the waffle paste wasn't well blended, skillet eggs were a tad cold. Not much of an issue actually, but after getting friendly greetings and hot food from the two nice ladies managing the food counter for 2 days, the comparison was too great not to mention.

Located next to El Paso International Airport, this hotel features an on-site restaurant and an outdoor pool with a seasonal 4-story waterslide. The El Paso Zoo is 10 minutes’ drive away.

The National Border Patrol Museum‎ is 20 minutes’ drive from the El Paso Airport Wyndham Hotel. El Paso city center is 7 mi away.

My room never got warm. It was cold evening and night. I set the heater on to warm up the room. It never did. When to the front desk to see if they could fix the issue. Again,  very friendly and said they would have someone look at it and fix the issue. Went to pick up wife at the airport and came back to the room to see the maintenance man working on the system. We left to have dinner and came back expecting to come back to a warm room. When got in the system was off and was set to 67°. I turned on the heater again and nothing but cold air again. My wife told me to turn it off and forgot about it because it was late and it was only for one night. So I did, we went to bed. 
Everything else was great except for the heater issue.

name: Radisson Hotel El Paso Airport
description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at Radisson Hotel El Paso Airport! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.
Located off Interstate 10, this hotel features spacious rooms with free Wi-Fi, a cable TV and DVD player.  A free shuttle is available to El Paso International Airport, less than 1 miles away.
A sofa bed and work desk are provided in all rooms at the Radisson Hotel El Paso Airport.  Each warmly decorated room includes a microwave, fridge and coffee maker.
On-site dining for all meals is available at Desert Pass restaurant, featuring Southwestern cuisine and handcrafted drinks.
An indoor pool and an outdoor pool are both available at the El Paso Airport Radisson Hotel, and guests can enjoy the relaxing hot tub.  A fitness room and business center are on site.
The El Paso Zoo and Butterfield Trail Golf Club are both within a 10-minute drive of the hotel.  The International Museum of Art is 6.4 miles away.

name: Hawthorn Suites by Wyndham El Paso
description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at Hawthorn Suites by Wyndham El Paso! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.
This Texas hotel provides free transportation to El Paso International Airport, 1 miles away. It features an outdoor pool, daily hot breakfast buffet and modern rooms with a 32-inch LCD TV. Guests of Booking.com will also receive a free coupon book for the nearby outlet shopping mall.
Free Wi-Fi, coffee facilities and a work desk are included in every room at El Paso Hawthorn Suites. They are styled in rich colors and have dark wood furniture.
A business center and a gym are on site. Hawthorn Suites by Wyndham El Paso also has a 24-hour front desk, daily maid service, free parking and bellman service.
The El Paso Zoo is just 4 miles from this hotel and Old Mission Trail is 10.4 miles away. Sun Bowl Stadium is 15 minutes away by car.

name: Best Western El Paso Airport Entrada Hotel
description:
Offering free shuttle service to and from El Paso International Airport, this hotel features free WiFi and a daily continental breakfast. Downtown El Paso is less than 8 miles away.
A large window and a wall-length mirror are found in each modern room of the Best Western El Paso Airport Entrada Hotel. Cable TV, a work desk and an iron are also provided. All rooms are nonsmoking.
The front desk of Best Western El Paso Airport Entrada Hotel is open at all times to help guests with needs. Free coffee is always available in the lobby. An early breakfast begins at 4:00 a.m.
The El Paso Zoo is less than 5 miles from the Best Western El Paso Airport Entrada Hotel. Western Playland Amusement Park is less than 15 miles away.

name: Marriott El Paso
description:
Adjacent to the El Paso International Airport, this hotel offers a free 24-hour airport shuttle. Enjoy the heated indoor/outdoor pool or work up a sweat in the fully-equipped fitness center.
The spacious rooms at the Marriott El Paso are furnished with pull-out desks, providing a flexible working area. Each bathroom features granite vanity tops and stone floors.
Guests can enjoy Southwestern dishes at the in house Red Rim Bistro.
Popular nearby attractions include the renowned El Paso Museum of Archaeology and the Centennial Museum and Chihuahuan Desert Gardens, both within a 15 minute drive from Marriott El Paso.

name: Comfort Inn & Suites I-10 Airport
description:
The Comfort Inn & Suites I-10 Airport hotel in El Paso, TX is conveniently located just one mile from El Paso International Airport. This El Paso, Texas hotel also offers easy access to Downtown El Paso, Fort Bliss and Juarez, Mexico.  Other nearby attractions include El Paso Zoo, Bowl El Paso, Sunland Park Racetrack, La Vina Winery
Business travelers will appreciate on-site business center conveniences like a computer with Internet and access to copy and fax services. There is a meeting room available, with the hotel able to accommodate up to 20 people for banquets and 15 people for conferences. Other amenities include free airport transportation, free hot breakfast, free wireless high-speed Internet access, free daily newspaper
All rooms offer a flat-screen television with cable, pillow top mattress, free local phone calls, hair dryer, desk, iron and ironing board. Some rooms feature a refrigerator, kitchen facilities and sofa sleeper.
Guest laundry service is available, as well as plenty of bus, car and truck parking. Pets are welcome for a small fee.
The Cielo Vista Mall and Fountains at Farrah are near the property.

userReviews.positive: I have stayed here twice because it is close to the Pearson Vue testing center.  I mostly love their pillows! They have hot breakfast and the facility is clean and always smells good.  There was a younger Hispanic man at the front desk who helped me both times I’ve stayed here and he’s always super nice and professional. Staying here as a young single female I feel comfortable in the hallways.  I’ve stayed other places in El Paso that were kind of sketchy and I like that they have indoor hallways and good lighting in the parking lot.  Their website says the deposit hold fee is $100 but I was only charged $50.  They’re always good about returning my fee.

name: Comfort Suites El Paso Airport
description:
Comfort Suites El Paso Airport offers free shuttle services to and from El Paso International Airport. The hotel offers free Wi-Fi, an outdoor pool and guest suites with cable TV.
Spacious suites provide a microwave and a refrigerator at this Comfort Suites in El Paso. Free local telephone calls can be made from each suite. Light wood furniture is included.
Guests have access to a fitness center at this hotel. A business center with free fax and photocopying services is also available. Long-term car parking is available behind the hotel. The hotel offers a complimentary breakfast buffet. Hotel shuttle service is available within 3 miles of the property to include shopping malls, restaurants and other places of interest.
Comfort Suites El Paso Airport is a 9-minute drive from the Fort Bliss Museum. The El Paso Zoo is 4.2 miles away.

name: Best Western Plus El Paso Airport Hotel & Conference Center
description:
Located less than 5 minutes’ drive from El Paso International Airport, this hotel is 1 miles from Cielo Vista Mall.  Guests can enjoy free Wi-Fi and connected indoor and outdoor pools.
Each room at the El Paso-Airport Best Western features cable TV as well as a seating area and tea- and coffee-making facilities.
Guests will find many amenities at this hotel, such as a fitness center, meeting and banquet facilities.
Gallery 3 Kitchen is located on site and offers American cuisine, and the El Agave bar is located in the hotel's lobby.
Best Western El Paso-Airport Hotel & Conference Center is 10 minutes’ drive from the center of El Paso, Texas.  The University of Texas at El Paso and Biggs Army Airfield are less than 15 minutes’ car ride from this hotel.

name: Newly Renovated - Hampton Inn & Suites El Paso-Airport
description:
Located just off Interstate-10, one mile from El Paso International Airport.
Complimentary buffet breakfast is served daily. A manager's reception with free drinks and snacks is offered on Tuesday and Wednesday evenings.
Guest rooms at the Hampton Inn in El Paso-Airport feature a work desk, coffee maker, microwave, mini-fridge, and cable flat-screen TV in every room.  Book a spacious apartment style suite featuring a bedroom with 1 king or 2 queen beds, living room with a sofa sleeper, and full kitchen. Airport transportation provided by complimentary ride share service from 6am-10pm.
Additional amenities at the Hampton Inn & Suites El Paso – Airport include in-house gym, business center, and Wireless HSIA throughout property,
El Paso Children's Hospital and Texas Tech University Health Sciences Center are within 9 minutes' drive of the property.

name: Fairfield Inn & Suites by Marriott El Paso Airport
description:
Offering an outdoor pool and a fitness center, Fairfield Inn & Suites El Paso Airport is located in El Paso. Free WiFi access is available and a complimentary breakfast is offered. Fort Bliss is less than 3.7 mi from the hotel.
Rooms here will provide you with a flat-screen cable TV and air conditioning. Featuring a bath or shower, private bathrooms also come with a hairdryer. Extras include a desk, bed linen and ironing facilities.
At Fairfield Inn & Suites El Paso Airport you will find a 24-hour front desk. Other facilities include a vending machine. The property offers free parking.
The hotel is 5.7 mi from El Paso Museum of Art and 5.2 mi from Wyler Aerial Tramway. El Paso International Airport is 1.9 mi away.

name: Best Western Sunland Park
description:
Located off Interstate 10, this El Paso hotel serves a daily continental breakfast and offers rooms with free WiFi and a cable TV.  The Sunland Park Racetrack and Casino is less than 1 miles away.
A microwave, fridge and coffee maker are provided in all rooms at the Best Western Sunland Park.  Each room offers simple décor and includes a seating area.
Free access to the seasonal outdoor pool is offered to all guests and a business center is on-site.  The hotel staff is available around the clock at the 24-hour front desk.
The Sunland Park Best Western is just 6.6 miles from the El Paso Museum of Art, and the El Paso Zoo is 9.7 miles away.  The El Paso International Airport is around a 20-minute drive from the hotel.

name: TownePlace Suites by Marriott El Paso Airport
description:
Offering an outdoor pool and a fitness center, TownePlace Suites by Marriott El Paso Airport is located 1.9 mi away from El Paso International Airport. Free WiFi access and a complimentary breakfast buffet are provided.
A flat-screen cable TV is features in every room at TownePlace Suites. There is a full kitchen with a dishwasher, coffee machine, refrigerator and a microwave. The private bathroom comes with a bath or shower.
A 24-hour front desk, barbecue facilities and a mini-market are available at TownePlace Suites by Marriott El Paso Airport. The property offers free parking.
The property serves complimentary beer and wine with a light meal Monday - Thursday from 5:30 pm - 7:30 pm.
The hotel is 5.8 mi from El Paso Museum of Art and 5.2 mi from Wyler Aerial Tramway.

name: Holiday Inn Express & Suites El Paso Airport, an IHG Hotel
description:
Located 1.4 miles from Cielo Vista Mall and 2 miles from El Paso International Airport, this hotel has a gym and an outdoor pool. Free Wi-Fi and free parking are available.
The rooms at the Holiday Inn Express & Suites El Paso Airport include cable TV, a tea/coffee maker, microwave and a private bathroom. Some rooms include a separate seating area.
The Holiday Inn Express & Suites El Paso Airport serves a breakfast consisting of hot and cold dishes and gourmet coffee.
The El Paso Airport Holiday Inn Express & Suites is 3.5 miles from Ascarate Park and 6.1 miles from the International Museum of Art. The hotel also offers an airport shuttle.
